annotationA: Trifunctional purine biosynthetic protein adenosine-3; Phosphoribosylglycinamide formyltransferase activity; methyltransferase activity; ATP binding; metal ion binding; phosphoribosylamine-glycine ligase activity; phosphoribosylformylglycinamidine cyclo-ligase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: purine nucleobase biosynthetic process; 'de novo' IMP biosynthetic process; In the central section; belongs to the AIR synthase family
annotationB: 40S ribosomal protein S20; Structural constituent of ribosome; RNA binding. It is involved in the biological process described with: translation
